    ers_dca_catches (
    message_id,start_timestamp,stop_timestamp,message_version,living_weight,species_fao_id,species_fiskeridir_id,species_group_id,species_main_group_id
   )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::BIGINT[],$2::TIMESTAMPTZ[],$3::TIMESTAMPTZ[],$4::INT[],$5::INT[],$6::TEXT[],$7::INT[],$8::INT[],$9::INT[]
    )
        ON CONFLICT (message_id,start_timestamp,stop_timestamp,species_fao_id) DO NOTHING
